Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:10.99,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}怖がってた 後ろの自分が 現実を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:16.68,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}今に映す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:22.06,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}いくつもの空を描いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:26.74,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}ここはきっと儚い心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:29.43,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:33.79,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}夢で 高く飛んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:40.15,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}体はどんな不安まとっても 振り払ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:44.48,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}守る 小さな思い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:46.68,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}広がりだして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.69,0:02:48.69,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}気づく 弱い私
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.69,0:02:50.73,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}君がいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:55.67,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}暗い世界 强くいれた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:03:01.13,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}長い夢見る心は そう永遠で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:05.31,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}I wanna always stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:10.85,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,1000)}I give you every thing I have
